54
00:04:29,936 --> 00:04:33,773
I may still be walking,
but they might as well have killed me.

55
00:04:35,483 --> 00:04:38,486
When people pass me,
I'm afraid they'll judge me and think,

56
00:04:38,987 --> 00:04:41,614
