204
00:14:12,810 --> 00:14:16,438
...went pheasant hunting over the weekend.

205
00:14:18,858 --> 00:14:21,068
And he stumbled upon a bizarre sight.

206
00:14:24,864 --> 00:14:27,366
The villager guiding the pheasant hunt

207
00:14:27,867 --> 00:14:30,493
