and not letting them escape?

212
00:14:46,594 --> 00:14:47,803
That seems suspicious.

213
00:14:50,347 --> 00:14:55,561
It all started when the investigation
into the forced labor began.

214
00:14:57,813 --> 00:14:59,981
REPORTER HEO SANG-CHEON
COVERED ON-SITE AT BROTHERS' HOME

215
00:14:59,982 --> 00:15:03,235
During the investigation, they realized
they had stumbled upon something major.

216
00:15:04,737 --> 00:15:09,074
And since I was in Busan,
they said I should check out the scene.

217
00:15:10,826 --> 00:15:13,412
That's where my coverage
of this case began.

218
00:15:17,207 --> 00:15:18,833
BEWARE OF DOG

219
00:15:18,834 --> 00:15:21,211
The first location I visited
was Banjeong Ranch in Ulsan.

220
00:15:21,879 --> 00:15:23,755
BANJEONG RANCH

221
00:15:23,756 --> 00:15:25,924
When I got closer to the scene,

222
00:15:25,925 --> 00:15:28,928
