00:31:16,082 --> 00:31:19,252
As citizens of the Olympic host nation

450
00:31:19,752 --> 00:31:22,129
and as citizens

451
00:31:22,130 --> 00:31:25,966
of a country emerging as a global player,

452
00:31:25,967 --> 00:31:29,345
we must earn the trust and respect

453
00:31:29,929 --> 00:31:33,057
