00:33:01,229 --> 00:33:04,357
when the police handed people over
to Brothers' Home.

479
00:33:07,151 --> 00:33:09,569
The names of police officers,
civil servants,

480
00:33:09,570 --> 00:33:12,239
and those who were captured were on them.

481
00:33:12,240 --> 00:33:13,448
BROTHERS' HOME INTAKE FORM

482
00:33:13,449 --> 00:33:17,537
They recorded when, where,
