711
00:48:24,192 --> 00:48:25,359
I'm not him.

712
00:48:25,360 --> 00:48:28,238
I don't know who Park Du-seon is.

713
00:48:29,364 --> 00:48:30,489
He's not here.

714
00:48:30,490 --> 00:48:31,909
- He's not?
- No.

715
00:48:32,409 --> 00:48:34,201
Who's Park In-geun?

716
00:48:34,202 --> 00:48:36,955
Mr. Park In-geun,
the director of Brothers' Home.

717
00:48:37,456 --> 00:48:39,958
