728
00:49:11,573 --> 00:49:14,993
They just want an apology.
Do you have no intention of apologizing?

729
00:49:15,661 --> 00:49:16,495
Sir?

730
00:49:19,331 --> 00:49:22,250
- They just want to hear an apology.
- What apology?

731
00:49:24,503 --> 00:49:26,463
Can't you just take a look at this
with me?

732
00:49:27,965 --> 00:49:28,798
Please?

733
00:49:28,799 --> 00:49:30,175
Let's go.

734
00:49:31,426 --> 00:49:32,969
I already have a passenger.

735
00:49:32,970 --> 00:49:34,179
Sorry.

736
00:49:35,639 --> 00:49:37,683
Sir, don't be like this.

737
00:49:40,769 --> 00:49:42,896
- This business won't last either.
- Seriously...

738
00:49:44,940 --> 00:49:46,941
But these people's lives have been ruined.

739
00:49:46,942 --> 00:49:49,318
What do they have to do with me?

740
00:49:49,319 --> 00:49:51,530
My life was ruined too.

741
00:49:53,490 --> 00:49:55,367
Why was your life ruined?

742
00:49:57,285 --> 00:49:59,287
The government acknowledged what happened.

743
00:50:00,205 --> 00:50:02,165
Over 600 people died.

744
00:50:03,667 --> 00:50:04,668
Sir.

745
00:50:05,794 --> 00:50:10,090
Over 600 people died in the institution
you and your father ran.

746
00:50:10,966 --> 00:50:12,676
You won't refute any of this?

747
00:50:13,176 --> 00:50:14,845
- No.
- You're not refuting it?

748
00:50:15,470 --> 00:50:16,471
Sir.

749
00:50:18,598 --> 00:50:19,599
Sir!

750
00:50:26,815 --> 00:50:29,151
All those vengeful souls.

751
00:50:30,902 --> 00:50:32,446
Aren't they afraid?

752
00:50:34,239 --> 00:50:36,074
If you so much as hurt someone,

753
00:50:37,159 --> 00:50:39,953
you'd normally feel guilty about it.

754
00:50:41,997 --> 00:50:44,624
His entire family

755
00:50:45,459 --> 00:50:48,003
took those people and exploited them

756
00:50:48,754 --> 00:50:52,174
to make money, using them as tools.

757
00:50:54,259 --> 00:50:57,554
Why do you think
he said he wasn't Park Du-seon?

758
00:51:00,432 --> 00:51:01,682
Mr. Jo, I'm sorry,

759
00:51:01,683 --> 00:51:04,602
can we resume in five minutes
after I smoke a cigarette?

760
00:51:04,603 --> 00:51:06,937
- Sure.
- That question makes me feel suffocated.

761
00:51:06,938 --> 00:51:07,897
Go ahead.

762
00:51:07,898 --> 00:51:09,649
Thank you. Sorry about that.

763
00:51:21,244 --> 00:51:23,872
I really don't understand it either.

764
00:51:25,457 --> 00:51:29,586
I don't understand
why they told such blatant lies

765
00:51:30,087 --> 00:51:32,421
when the truth could be easily revealed.

766
00:51:32,422 --> 00:51:35,383
In my view, Brothers' Home

767
00:51:36,009 --> 00:51:37,551
was the perpetrator.

768
00:51:37,552 --> 00:51:38,595
But I believe

769
00:51:39,346 --> 00:51:40,597
the Korean government

770
00:51:41,556 --> 00:51:45,476
is most responsible for what happened,

771
00:51:45,477 --> 00:51:47,353
as they gave the orders.

772
00:51:47,354 --> 00:51:48,688
Instead of just me,

773
00:51:49,481 --> 00:51:52,234
the son of Director Park In-geun,
stepping up,

774
00:51:52,984 --> 00:51:56,279
the government should also say,

775
00:51:56,780 --> 00:51:59,116
"Yes, these things were wrong back then."

776
00:51:59,616 --> 00:52:01,159
They should own up to it

777
00:52:02,077 --> 00:52:03,745
and offer sincere apologies.

778
00:52:04,871 --> 00:52:06,123
That's what I think.

779
00:52:08,250 --> 00:52:09,251
Once again,

780
00:52:11,002 --> 00:52:12,546
I would like to extend...

781
00:52:16,383 --> 00:52:17,509
my apologies

782
00:52:18,510 --> 00:52:22,597
to the victims and their families

783
00:52:23,348 --> 00:52:25,976
who suffered during their time...

784
00:52:29,396 --> 00:52:31,648
at Brothers' Home,

785
00:52:33,066 --> 00:52:36,111
and for all the pain
they've endured since.

786
00:52:45,370 --> 00:52:48,331
From my perspective,
this is not a genuine apology.

787
00:52:51,626 --> 00:52:53,919
A true, genuine apology

788
00:52:53,920 --> 00:52:57,673
should include specific measures
he will take

789
00:52:57,674 --> 00:52:59,633
to make amends.

790
00:52:59,634 --> 00:53:02,303
This is nothing but...

791
00:53:02,304 --> 00:53:05,139
All I'm hearing are excuses,
blaming the police,

792
00:53:05,140 --> 00:53:07,017
the government, and the city of Busan.

